    <refsect1 xml:id="description"><title>Description</title>
        <para>
            <function>log2</function> returns the base 2 logarithm of <parameter>x</parameter>. i.e., the value
            <inlineequation><mml:math xmlns:mml="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" overflow="scroll"><mml:mi>y</mml:mi></mml:math></inlineequation> which satisfies
            <inlineequation><mml:math xmlns:mml="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" overflow="scroll"><mml:apply><mml:eq definitionURL="" encoding=""/><mml:mi>x</mml:mi><mml:mrow><mml:msup><mml:mi>2</mml:mi><mml:mi>y</mml:mi></mml:msup></mml:mrow></mml:apply></mml:math></inlineequation>.
            Results are undefined if <inlineequation><mml:math xmlns:mml="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" overflow="scroll"><mml:apply><mml:leq definitionURL="" encoding=""/><mml:mi>x</mml:mi><mml:mn>0</mml:mn></mml:apply></mml:math></inlineequation>.
        </para>
    </refsect1>
